        <p>
          How many subsets <m>\{a,b,c\}</m> are there of <m>\{2,3,4,\ldots\}</m> such that <m>abc = 2 \cdot 3 \cdot 5 \cdot 7 \cdot 11 \cdot 13 \cdot 17</m>?
        </p>
      </statement>
    </exercise>

    <exercise>
